


	
        Email tip: If they didn't get your message, then they won't know that they didn't get it          Raymond Chen        
            
            May 6th, 20080 0
		
        I illustrate this point with a conversation that actually happened:
 Person 1: “Did you get my email?”
 Person 2: “Which one?”
 Person 1: “The last one.” 

        
                

        
		
                

            
            
                
